CARMEN MILLER v. THAMES VALLEY COUNCIL FOR COMMUNITY ACTION ET AL. (13914)

Dupont, C. J., and Poti and Heiman, Js.

Argued November 30 decision released December 19, 1995 Ronald M. Christensen, for the appellant (plaintiff). Lucas D. Strunk, with whom, on the brief, was Margaret E. Corrigan, for the appellees (defendants). PER CURIAM.

The decision of the compensation review board is affirmed.
